dc_description_s: Link to download of Wiscland 2 land cover data (does not include accuracy datasets, which can be found here: https://www.arcgis.com/home/item.html?id=febda01fbe3e4e0bbd4c5938c1490322) The Wiscland 2 land cover project was a collaborative effort of the WI Department of Natural Resources (WDNR), University of Wisconsin-Madison (UW), and the WI State Cartographer's Office (SCO) conducted between the fall of 2013 and August 2016.  For more information read the metadata provided with the dataset.        *to download this item from the DNR Open Data Portal, simply visit the item and your browser will automatically prompt you to download it.
